column1: 2/06/10 Arkansas State Powerlifting and Bench Press Championship Rogers, Arkansas

We would like to take a minute and thank Terry Tucker (Meet Director) for a great job putting this meet together and Also Thanks to Jeff Phillips, Jamie McDougal and all the Top Hogs for great job with the judging, loading, Spotting, and running a very well ran platform. Patrica Cuttingham also done a great job on the score table, couldn't have made it without her. Thanks to everyone that took put and or came out to support the meet. Hope to see everyone soon.. Jesse
